headline.main: France's Fillon Does Not Say Whether He Will Step Down or Not in Rally Speech
headline.print_headline: France's Fillon Does Not Say Whether He Will Step Down or Not in Rally Speech

lead_paragraph: Under-fire French presidential candidate Francois Fillon on Sunday gave a defiant 28-minute speech to a rally of thousands of supporters in Paris in which he did not say whether he would continue his campaign or not.
